---
title: Thai Yellow Beef Meatball Curry with Charred Courgette and Jasmine Rice
description: We love good Thai Yellow Beef Meatball Curry & Rice and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
